Tesco Plc &lt;TSCO.L> said that &lt;CountyLtd> had yesterday bought on its behalf 2.06 mln shares, oraround 4.2 pct, in &lt;Hillards Plc> for between 302p and 310p ashare.    Tesco yesterday launched a 151.4 mln stg bid for the northof England supermarket chain, which Hillards promptly rejected.    Hillards shares were last quoted at 324p, compared withlast night's close of 313p. REUTER&#3;